{
  "video_id": "aGedUxTAfBk",
  "title": "The Purpose of Friendship",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1500.0,
      "end_time": 3780.0,
      "text": "friendship should be one of the high points of existence"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3780.0,
      "end_time": 5880.0,
      "text": "and yet it's also the most routinely disappointing thing we have to deal with."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 9000.0,
      "end_time": 11639.0,
      "text": "Too often you're at supper at someone's house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 11639.0,
      "end_time": 13410.0,
      "text": "there's an impressive spread and the hosts have evidently gone to a lot of trouble."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 17580.0,
      "end_time": 19289.0,
      "text": "But the conversation is meandering and"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19289.0,
      "end_time": 21930.0,
      "text": "devoid of any real interest it flits"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 21930.0,
      "end_time": 23640.0,
      "text": "from an overlong description of the"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 23640.0,
      "end_time": 25890.0,
      "text": "failings of the in-flight service on a"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 25890.0,
      "end_time": 28529.0,
      "text": "particular airline to a strangely heated"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 28529.0,
      "end_time": 30840.0,
      "text": "discussion about the tax code. The"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 30840.0,
      "end_time": 32790.0,
      "text": "intentions of the hosts are hugely"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 32790.0,
      "end_time": 35520.0,
      "text": "touching, but as so often we go home"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 35520.0,
      "end_time": 37170.0,
      "text": "wondering what on earth the whole"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 37170.0,
      "end_time": 40620.0,
      "text": "performance was really about. The key to"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 40620.0,
      "end_time": 42600.0,
      "text": "the problem of friendship is to be found"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 42600.0,
      "end_time": 45660.0,
      "text": "in an odd sounding place: a lack of a"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 45660.0,
      "end_time": 48149.0,
      "text": "sense of purpose. Our attempts at"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 48149.0,
      "end_time": 50430.0,
      "text": "friendship tend to go adrift because we"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 50430.0,
      "end_time": 52320.0,
      "text": "collectively resist the task of"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 52320.0,
      "end_time": 54360.0,
      "text": "developing a clear picture of what"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 54360.0,
      "end_time": 57120.0,
      "text": "friendship might really be for."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 57120.0,
      "end_time": 58440.0,
      "text": "The problem is that we're unfairly"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 58440.0,
      "end_time": 60120.0,
      "text": "uncomfortable with the idea of"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 60120.0,
      "end_time": 62730.0,
      "text": "friendship having any declared purpose,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 62730.0,
      "end_time": 65430.0,
      "text": "because we associate purpose with the"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 65430.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67619.0,
      "text": "least attractive and most cynical of"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 67619.0,
      "end_time": 70320.0,
      "text": "motives.  Yet purpose doesn't have to ruin"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 70320.0,
      "end_time": 72720.0,
      "text": "friendship and in fact the more we"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 72720.0,
      "end_time": 74580.0,
      "text": "define what a friendship might be for"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 74580.0,
      "end_time": 76860.0,
      "text": "the more we can focus in on what we"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 76860.0,
      "end_time": 78659.0,
      "text": "should be doing with every person in our"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 78659.0,
      "end_time": 80880.0,
      "text": "lives, or indeed the more we can"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 80880.0,
      "end_time": 82979.0,
      "text": "helpfully conclude that we shouldn't be"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 82979.0,
      "end_time": 84240.0,
      "text": "with them at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 84240.0,
      "end_time": 86640.0,
      "text": "There are at least four things we might"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 86640.0,
      "end_time": 88799.0,
      "text": "be trying to do with the people we know."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 88799.0,
      "end_time": 92100.0,
      "text": "Firstly, networking. It's an unfairly"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 92100.0,
      "end_time": 94799.0,
      "text": "maligned idea. We're small, fragile"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 94799.0,
      "end_time": 97560.0,
      "text": "creatures in a vast world. Our individual"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 97560.0,
      "end_time": 100259.0,
      "text": "capacities are entirely insufficient to"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 100259.0,
      "end_time": 102540.0,
      "text": "realize the demands of our imaginations."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 102540.0,
      "end_time": 105060.0,
      "text": "So of course we need collaborators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 105060.0,
      "end_time": 107310.0,
      "text": "accomplices who can align their"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 107310.0,
      "end_time": 109380.0,
      "text": "abilities and energies with ours."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 109380.0,
      "end_time": 111539.0,
      "text": "This idea of friendship was given a lot"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 111539.0,
      "end_time": 113969.0,
      "text": "of space in classical literature."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 113969.0,
      "end_time": 115860.0,
      "text": "Take the Argonauts, the legendary ancient"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 115860.0,
      "end_time": 118110.0,
      "text": "Greek tale, which traced how a heroic"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 118110.0,
      "end_time": 121020.0,
      "text": "captain called Jason networked in order to"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 121020.0,
      "end_time": 123240.0,
      "text": "assemble a band of friends to sail on"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 123240.0,
      "end_time": 125070.0,
      "text": "the Arkham, in search of the Golden"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 125070.0,
      "end_time": 128009.0,
      "text": "Fleece. Later, the same idea emerged when"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 128008.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130348.99999999999,
      "text": "Jesus networked, to put together a band of"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 130348.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132239.0,
      "text": "twelve disciples with whom he could"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 132239.0,
      "end_time": 134489.0,
      "text": "spread one or two world-changing ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 134489.0,
      "end_time": 136680.0,
      "text": "about forgiveness and compassion. Rather"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 136680.0,
      "end_time": 138780.0,
      "text": "than diminish our own efforts as we hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 138780.0,
      "end_time": 140880.0,
      "text": "out our business cards, such prestigious"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 140880.0,
      "end_time": 143190.0,
      "text": "examples can show how elevated an"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 143190.0,
      "end_time": 145530.0,
      "text": "ambitious networking friendships could"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 145530.0,
      "end_time": 149790.0,
      "text": "ideally be. Secondly, reassurance. The"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 149790.0,
      "end_time": 152190.0,
      "text": "human condition is full of terror. We're"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 152190.0,
      "end_time": 154470.0,
      "text": "always on the verge of disgrace, danger"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 154470.0,
      "end_time": 156840.0,
      "text": "and disappointment and yet, such are the"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 156840.0,
      "end_time": 158849.0,
      "text": "rules of polite conduct that we're"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 158849.0,
      "end_time": 160890.0,
      "text": "permanently in danger of imagining that"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 160890.0,
      "end_time": 163620.0,
      "text": "we are the only ones to be as crazy as"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 163620.0,
      "end_time": 166200.0,
      "text": "we know we are. We badly need friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 166200.0,
      "end_time": 168060.0,
      "text": "because with the people we know only"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 168060.0,
      "end_time": 169620.0,
      "text": "superficially, there are few"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 169620.0,
      "end_time": 172500.0,
      "text": "confessions of sexual compulsion or of"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 172500.0,
      "end_time": 175200.0,
      "text": "regret, rage and confusion. These"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 175200.0,
      "end_time": 177090.0,
      "text": "superficial acquaintances refuse to"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 177090.0,
      "end_time": 179100.0,
      "text": "admit that they, too, are going slightly"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 179100.0,
      "end_time": 181950.0,
      "text": "out of their minds. Yet the reassuring"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 181950.0,
      "end_time": 184260.0,
      "text": "true friend gives us access to a very"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 184260.0,
      "end_time": 186420.0,
      "text": "necessary and accurate sense of their"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 186420.0,
      "end_time": 189359.0,
      "text": "own humiliations and follies, insights"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 189359.0,
      "end_time": 191040.0,
      "text": "with which we can begin to judge"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 191040.0,
      "end_time": 193440.0,
      "text": "ourselves and our sad and compulsive"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 193440.0,
      "end_time": 196019.0,
      "text": "lives slightly more compassionately."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 196019.0,
      "end_time": 200010.0,
      "text": "Thirdly, fun. Despite talk of hedonism and"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 200010.0,
      "end_time": 202380.0,
      "text": "immediate gratification, life gives us"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 202380.0,
      "end_time": 204450.0,
      "text": "constant lessons in the need to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 204450.0,
      "end_time": 205560.0,
      "text": "serious."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 205560.0,
      "end_time": 207660.0,
      "text": "We have to guard our dignity, avoid"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 207660.0,
      "end_time": 210030.0,
      "text": "looking like a fool and pass as a mature"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 210030.0,
      "end_time": 213000.0,
      "text": "adult. The pressure can become onerous"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 213000.0,
      "end_time": 215940.0,
      "text": "and in the end even dangerous. That's why"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 215940.0,
      "end_time": 218370.0,
      "text": "we constantly need access to people we"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 218370.0,
      "end_time": 220799.0,
      "text": "can trust enough to be silly with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 220799.0,
      "end_time": 223170.0,
      "text": "They might most of the time be training"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 223170.0,
      "end_time": 225420.0,
      "text": "to be a neurosurgeon or advising middle"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 225420.0,
      "end_time": 226829.0,
      "text": "sized companies about their tax"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 226829.0,
      "end_time": 229500.0,
      "text": "liabilities, but when we're together we"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 229500.0,
      "end_time": 232560.0,
      "text": "can be therapeutically daft. We can put"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 232560.0,
      "end_time": 235500.0,
      "text": "on accents, share lewd fantasies or doodle"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 235500.0,
      "end_time": 237540.0,
      "text": "on the newspaper, adding a huge nose and"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 237540.0,
      "end_time": 239100.0,
      "text": "a missing front tooth to the President"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 239100.0,
      "end_time": 241440.0,
      "text": "or giving the fashion model distended"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 241440.0,
      "end_time": 242630.0,
      "text": "ears and masses of"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 242630.0,
      "end_time": 245660.0,
      "text": "curly hair. The fun friend solves the"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 245660.0,
      "end_time": 248210.0,
      "text": "problem of shame around important but"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 248210.0,
      "end_time": 250880.0,
      "text": "unprestigious sides of ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 250880.0,
      "end_time": 254720.0,
      "text": "Fourthly, clarifying our minds. To a"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 254720.0,
      "end_time": 256970.0,
      "text": "surprising degree it's very hard to"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 256970.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258739.00000000003,
      "text": "think on our own."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 258738.99999999997,
      "end_time": 261589.99999999997,
      "text": "The mind is skittish and squeamish. As a"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 261589.99999999997,
      "end_time": 264170.0,
      "text": "result, many issues lie confused within"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 264170.0,
      "end_time": 266840.0,
      "text": "us. We feel angry but are not sure why."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 266840.0,
      "end_time": 269210.0,
      "text": "Something is wrong with our job but we"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 269210.0,
      "end_time": 271700.0,
      "text": "can't pin it down. The thinking friend"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 271700.0,
      "end_time": 274430.0,
      "text": "holds us to the task. They ask gentle"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 274430.0,
      "end_time": 276590.0,
      "text": "but probing questions which act as a"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 276590.0,
      "end_time": 279110.0,
      "text": "mirror that assist us with the task of"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 279110.0,
      "end_time": 282500.0,
      "text": "knowing ourselves. One side effect of"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 282500.0,
      "end_time": 284150.0,
      "text": "getting a bit more precise about what"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 284150.0,
      "end_time": 285710.0,
      "text": "we're trying to do with our social lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 285710.0,
      "end_time": 288140.0,
      "text": "is that we're likely to conclude that in"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 288140.0,
      "end_time": 290000.0,
      "text": "many cases, we're spending time with"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 290000.0,
      "end_time": 293060.0,
      "text": "people for no truly identifiable good"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 293060.0,
      "end_time": 295940.0,
      "text": "reason. These proto friends share none of"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 295940.0,
      "end_time": 297920.0,
      "text": "our professional ambitions or interests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 297920.0,
      "end_time": 300410.0,
      "text": "they aren't reassuring and may indeed be"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 300410.0,
      "end_time": 302420.0,
      "text": "secretly really very excited by the"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 302420.0,
      "end_time": 304700.0,
      "text": "possibility of failure. We can't be"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 304700.0,
      "end_time": 306890.0,
      "text": "catharticly silly around them and they"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 306890.0,
      "end_time": 308270.0,
      "text": "aren't the least bit interested in"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 308270.0,
      "end_time": 310910.0,
      "text": "furthering our or their path to self"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 310910.0,
      "end_time": 313370.0,
      "text": "knowledge. They are, like so many of the"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 313370.0,
      "end_time": 315890.0,
      "text": "people in our social lives, simply in our"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 315890.0,
      "end_time": 318350.0,
      "text": "orbit as a result of some unhappy"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 318350.0,
      "end_time": 320390.0,
      "text": "accident that we've been too sentimental"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 320390.0,
      "end_time": 323780.0,
      "text": "to correct. We should dare to be a little"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 323780.0,
      "end_time": 326120.0,
      "text": "ruthless in this area. Culling"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 326120.0,
      "end_time": 328070.0,
      "text": "acquaintances isn't a sign that we've"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 328070.0,
      "end_time": 330470.0,
      "text": "lost belief in friendship, it's evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
